Name:                c0parser
Version:             0.2
Synopsis:            Simple C0 Parser
Description:         The package contains a parser for C0 programs.
	             The C0-language is introduced in the basic programming course \"Algorithmisches Denken und imperative Programmierung\" (WS 2012/13 and later) at the University of Bonn.
License:             GPL
Author:              Daniel Seidel
Maintainer:          ds@iai.uni-bonn.de
Build-Type:          Simple
Cabal-Version:       >=1.2
Category:            Language
Stability:           Experimental

Library
  hs-source-dirs:    src
  Exposed-Modules:   Language.C0.Parser.C0Parser,
                     Language.C0.Types.C0Types
  Build-Depends:     base >= 3 && < 6,
                     parsec >= 3 && <4
